CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Frogs' Guests - Getting a bang out of the annual Frog formal held at Gateway Plaza were these interesting guests. Seated: Atty. and Mrs. Paul Simmons, Monongahela; Mr. and Mrs. C. L. Bynum, Columbus, Ohio, and Mr. and Mrs. Albert Smith, Pittsburgh. Standing: Atty. and Mrs. Linn Washington, Mrs. Gladys McKinney, and Atty. and Mrs. George Shields. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left, standing: Atty. and Mrs. Linn Washington, Gladys McKinney, and Atty. and Mrs. George Shields; seated: Atty. and Mrs. Paul Simmons, Mr. and Mrs. C. L. Bynum, and Mr. and Mrs. Albert Smith, gathered around banquet table in Gateway Plaza for FROGS event
